{"batchNumber":75,"issues":[{"number":3030,"title":"spring-ai-bedrock-converse-spring-boot-starter is missing in pring-ai-bom 1.0.0-M8","body":"The dependency \n```\n<dependency>\n  <groupId>org.springframework.ai</groupId>\n  <artifactId>spring-ai-bedrock-converse-spring-boot-starter</artifactId>\n</dependency>\n```\nis missing in \n```\n<dependency>\n  <groupId>org.springframework.ai</groupId>\n  <artifactId>spring-ai-bom</artifactId>\n  <version>1.0.0-M8</version>\n  <type>pom</type>\n  <scope>import</scope>\n</dependency>\n```","state":"CLOSED","createdAt":[2025,5,7,16,14,59],"updatedAt":[2025,5,15,7,23,43],"closedAt":[2025,5,15,7,23,43],"url":"https://github.com/spring-projects/spring-ai/issues/3030","author":{"login":"brunorabaca","name":""},"comments":[{"author":{"login":"dafriz","name":"David Frizelle"},"body":"From M6 to M7 there were artifact id changes for the model starters:\n\nspring-ai-{model}-spring-boot-starter → spring-ai-starter-model-{model}\n\nTry this instead\n\n```\n<dependency>\n  <groupId>org.springframework.ai</groupId>\n  <artifactId>spring-ai-starter-model-bedrock-converse</artifactId>\n</dependency>\n```\n","createdAt":[2025,5,8,12,8,47]},{"author":{"login":"brunorabaca","name":""},"body":"Thank you @dafriz it worked.","createdAt":[2025,5,12,15,23,41]}],"labels":[]},{"number":3029,"title":"Remove Hana autoconfiguration","body":"","state":"CLOSED","createdAt":[2025,5,7,15,28,29],"updatedAt":[2025,5,8,15,59,30],"closedAt":[2025,5,8,15,59,29],"url":"https://github.com/spring-projects/spring-ai/issues/3029","author":{"login":"markpollack","name":"Mark Pollack"},"comments":[],"labels":[]},{"number":3028,"title":"Review Dependency Structure Matrix","body":"Diagonalize the Matrix!","state":"CLOSED","createdAt":[2025,5,7,15,27,36],"updatedAt":[2025,5,11,16,42,40],"closedAt":[2025,5,11,16,42,39],"url":"https://github.com/spring-projects/spring-ai/issues/3028","author":{"login":"markpollack","name":"Mark Pollack"},"comments":[{"author":{"login":"ilayaperumalg","name":"Ilayaperumal Gopinathan"},"body":"This is addressed via ebfa5b9b2cc2ab0d20e25dc6128c4b1c9c327f89","createdAt":[2025,5,9,11,3,36]},{"author":{"login":"markpollack","name":"Mark Pollack"},"body":"There are more modules to do, it was only done for spring-ai-commons and spring-ai-model.","createdAt":[2025,5,9,20,2,38]},{"author":{"login":"markpollack","name":"Mark Pollack"},"body":"This look ok for the spring-ai-chat-client as well.  ","createdAt":[2025,5,11,16,42,39]}],"labels":[]}],"timestamp":"2025-07-23_12-16-41"}